creator: BulkLoads.com
descriptionHtml:
Bulkloads.com is a community of shippers, carriers, and brokers in the bulk commodity trucking industry. Our shipper members consist of logistics managers in grain, fertilizer, aggregates, feed ingredients, and all other agricultural commodities.
Our carrier members pull a variety of trailers including hopper bottoms, walking floors, end dump trailers, belt trailers, and live floors.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Added a scanning feature to scan and send load documents.
- Added a document management feature to view documents sent and received.
- Various speed and reliability updates.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New 'My Freight' features added.
- Ability to submit loads for payment and automatically create invoices.
- View your invoices and record payments on them or get alerted when you've been paid.
- Drivers and Owner Operators can now be dispatched loads in the app. View all of your booked loads, update the status, weights, scan documents and submit for payment.
- View load offers sent to you in the app.
- Automatically book loads in the app with a click of a button!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Load Tracking is now available!
You can now enable location tracking on your assigned loads in the BulkLoads app so your dispatcher can keep track of your location as you're delivering a load. Once the load is delivered you can easily stop the tracking with a click of a button.
100% privacy first. YOU decide when to start and stop tracking. We never track you without your permission and we do not keep past location records.
